channel.description:

[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "3 226 3223" at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:1279) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:23) at server.main(server.java:27)[/code]

Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. :: Done! Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
help me out here? EDIT: soz for duble post Also, sorry for the misleading title (LoL)
